parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag system can cause the airbags to deploy improperly, leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: no airbag deployment in a crash

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbags did not deploy in a crash

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Stabilitrak system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to a crash.
symptoms: Stabilitrak off light flashed on the dashboard
vehicle shut down on the highway.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in repairing the airbag recall can lead to a continued risk of injury or death.
symptoms: No remedy available for the airbag recall
manufacturer exceeded a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking and structural failure of the dashboard can lead to a compromised airbag deployment, potentially causing injuries or fatalities. Additionally, loose plastic pieces can interfere with brake and accelerator pedals, posing a risk to vehicle safety.
symptoms: often near the airbag or instrument panel
which can progress and worsen over time. In some cases
the dashboard may collapse or break apart
causing loose plastic pieces to fall off.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Chrome Peeling and Door Handle Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The peeling of chrome from door handles can cause cuts and injuries to occupants. Additionally, the failure of door handles can lead to difficulties in entering or exiting the vehicle.
symptoms: Peeling or flaking of chrome from door handles
which can cause cuts or injuries. In some cases
the door handles may break off entirely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power liftgate can cause injuries or trapping of occupants, particularly children.
symptoms: The power liftgate may not open or close properly
or may close on an occupant's hand.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various issues, including loss of power, faulty gauges, and malfunctioning lights, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: ABS and Stabilitrack lights come on

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause airbags to deploy unexpectedly or not deploy at all in the event of a crash, leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: airbags do not deploy in a crash

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cracks in the dashboard can cause airbags to deploy unexpectedly, and faulty instrument panels can lead to loss of critical information, increasing the risk of accidents.
The failure of the brake system can cause loss of braking power, increasing the risk of accidents.
